{"tid":1442780,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"得推同表情會簡略顯示短回覆其實唔係好夠","createTime":"2019-08-11T05:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T13:40:12.000Z","uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fc17d3649f0cd6a5e8121a48a78ab6e4f149e6e8","tid":1442780,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"有呢個功能之後的確睇post觀感好好多<br />\n<br />\n但依家啲推土機唔止係用表情、「推」、「push」<br />\n<br />\n好似之前「我冇野講」、呢排熱門又一堆721推post<br />\n<br />\n結果都係治標唔治本影響體驗<br />\n<br />\n有冇方法可以將嗰期熱門出現最多短句自動簡短<br />\n<br />\n或者俾我地自己set邊啲短句簡短顯示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114a201c242087310ae9c6ce6954bc2a0f12261c","tid":1442780,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:15:58.000Z","msg":"連狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314235fa25d46d44dd4c5418e1180d78c504f7c0","tid":1442780,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8075e4284e01fda06dea340d0c02a2c21740c058","tid":1442780,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e41b22d49b84b13d4fb842500f6497dbaa8b02ce","tid":1442780,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:38:49.000Z","msg":"連狗入一入嚟plz"},{"pid":"c1e03248a3d770e47bba6385a4aac3a27eb5ce54","tid":1442780,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:39:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0c42aad799ba7121e284c1af6a8f4ea9d25c8c","tid":1442780,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1e03248a3d77